data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, FEBRUARY 3RD 1PM-3PM***Welcome to your dream home! This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom end unit offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Step inside to discover abundant natural light, an open floor plan and a cool garage-style door that seamlessly connects indoor and outdoor spaces – an ideal setting for entertaining friends and family. Or stay cozy during the colder months with an electric fireplace that not only provides warmth but also adds ambiance with its customizable colors and heat modes. This spacious layout features a large laundry room, a 2-car garage, and a convenient pocket office, providing you with ample space for both work and relaxation. The kitchen is a chef's delight with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a generous island, making meal preparation a joy.  Experience the benefits of energy efficiency with low monthly Xcel payments, even with above-average use. The home's thoughtful design extends to its accessibility, easily reaching E-470 and DIA for hassle-free commuting. For outdoor enthusiasts, enjoy being close to bike and walking paths, as well as nearby dog parks and community parks for young families. Take advantage of walking distance to nearby restaurants, breweries, and businesses, with daily food trucks and entertainment for relaxing evenings out. Experience low ownership maintenance with complete HOA support, relieving you of yard responsibilities while making entertaining a breeze. The community is known for its warmth, support, and attentive neighbors, creating a truly welcoming environment. This neighborhood strikes the perfect balance – quiet and peaceful, making it an ideal haven. Welcome to more than just a house – a place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your own!
